  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330810/extras/ab7a7a0413038dfadad208bbcceda4ce.poster.avif?t=1761276276\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330810/extras/ab7a7a0413038dfadad208bbcceda4ce.webm?t=1761276276\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330810/extras/ab7a7a0413038dfadad208bbcceda4ce.mp4?t=1761276276\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Alien Frontier is an open world, third-person shooter roguelite. Explore, search, and mine resources in the deadly alien wilderness... assuming you can survive combat with hordes of bloodthirsty aliens. Collect loot and upgrades to become the most dangerous (and wealthy) prospector in the galaxy!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330810/extras/Frenetic_Combat.gif?t=1677231837?t=1761276276\" /></span><br>Grapple, dash, glide, and hover your way through harrowing encounters with the deadly alien fauna. Fight your way through adrenaline-fueled, bullet hell inspired third-person combat that will keep you on the edge of your seat.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330810/extras/fe85e8b272d42f1a6439400e2405b12d.poster.avif?t=1761276276\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330810/extras/fe85e8b272d42f1a6439400e2405b12d.webm?t=1761276276\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330810/extras/fe85e8b272d42f1a6439400e2405b12d.mp4?t=1761276276\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>With over 100 unique items, upgrades, and abilities, each run is a chance to discover and combine loot in creative and unexpected ways, allowing you to unleash devastating power on even the most fearsome of aliens.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330810/extras/81a70d10256508f485b9b74cd2f7dcd7.poster.avif?t=1761276276\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330810/extras/81a70d10256508f485b9b74cd2f7dcd7.webm?t=1761276276\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330810/extras/81a70d10256508f485b9b74cd2f7dcd7.mp4?t=1761276276\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>As an interstellar prospector, you don't just explore a vast open world, but you change it. From constructing tunnels deep into mountains to setting up massive mining rigs on the surface, every structure you build transforms the landscape and rewards you with valuable upgrades and equipment.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330810/extras/af4cb9bf9ade1ee0ed90e85a12ed37a6.poster.avif?t=1761276276\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330810/extras/af4cb9bf9ade1ee0ed90e85a12ed37a6.webm?t=1761276276\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330810/extras/af4cb9bf9ade1ee0ed90e85a12ed37a6.mp4?t=1761276276\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Use your jetpack, thrusters, and hoverboard to explore procedural open worlds where there are no minimaps to guide you. Read the landscape and explore every corner of the world to uncover the mystery of the strange alien planet.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330810/extras/ab7a7a0413038dfadad208bbcceda4ce.poster.avif?t=1761276276\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330810/extras/ab7a7a0413038dfadad208bbcceda4ce.webm?t=1761276276\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330810/extras/ab7a7a0413038dfadad208bbcceda4ce.mp4?t=1761276276\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Alien Frontier is an open world, third-person shooter roguelite. Explore, search, and mine resources in the deadly alien wilderness... assuming you can survive combat with hordes of bloodthirsty aliens. Collect loot and upgrades to become the most dangerous (and wealthy) prospector in the galaxy!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330810/extras/Frenetic_Combat.gif?t=1677231837?t=1761276276\" /></span><br>Grapple, dash, glide, and hover your way through harrowing encounters with the deadly alien fauna. Fight your way through adrenaline-fueled, bullet hell inspired third-person combat that will keep you on the edge of your seat.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330810/extras/fe85e8b272d42f1a6439400e2405b12d.poster.avif?t=1761276276\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330810/extras/fe85e8b272d42f1a6439400e2405b12d.webm?t=1761276276\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330810/extras/fe85e8b272d42f1a6439400e2405b12d.mp4?t=1761276276\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>With over 100 unique items, upgrades, and abilities, each run is a chance to discover and combine loot in creative and unexpected ways, allowing you to unleash devastating power on even the most fearsome of aliens.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330810/extras/81a70d10256508f485b9b74cd2f7dcd7.poster.avif?t=1761276276\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330810/extras/81a70d10256508f485b9b74cd2f7dcd7.webm?t=1761276276\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330810/extras/81a70d10256508f485b9b74cd2f7dcd7.mp4?t=1761276276\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>As an interstellar prospector, you don't just explore a vast open world, but you change it. From constructing tunnels deep into mountains to setting up massive mining rigs on the surface, every structure you build transforms the landscape and rewards you with valuable upgrades and equipment.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330810/extras/af4cb9bf9ade1ee0ed90e85a12ed37a6.poster.avif?t=1761276276\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330810/extras/af4cb9bf9ade1ee0ed90e85a12ed37a6.webm?t=1761276276\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330810/extras/af4cb9bf9ade1ee0ed90e85a12ed37a6.mp4?t=1761276276\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Use your jetpack, thrusters, and hoverboard to explore procedural open worlds where there are no minimaps to guide you. Read the landscape and explore every corner of the world to uncover the mystery of the strange alien planet.